org.beanfabrics.event

Interface ListListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.util.EventListener
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    WeakListListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ListAdapter, WeakListAdapter

    public interface ListListener
extends java.util.EventListener
    The listener interface for receiving ListEvents.

    A listener object created from this class can be registered with a IListPM using the IListPM.addListListener(ListListener) method.

    Author:
    Michael Karneim
